## Review Commands

```bash
cat argocd/application.yaml
k8s-forge doctor
```

If ArgoCD is installed manually later, review the manifest and apply it yourself. `k8s-forge` intentionally does not run `kubectl apply` or `argocd app sync`.

## Private Repositories

Private repository credentials must be configured manually in ArgoCD. `k8s-forge` never generates Git credentials, GitHub secrets, ArgoCD secrets, tokens, or passwords.

## Scope v0.10.0

- ArgoCD `Application` only;
- no `AppProject`;
- Helm source only;
- no Flux support;
- no automatic sync;
- no Git push;
- no cluster modification.
